Would you guys have joined moparisthebest if kaitnieks didn't shut down? Please leave a comment and be honest. I would join both seeing as i came here first and I've heard alot of good things about kaitnieks.
You are probably gonna say moparisthebest wouldnt have made this site if kaitnieks didnt shut down, now im just infering that mopar would have done it if kaitnieks had or had not shut down.
